text: Self-described psychic Sylvia Browne predicted a 2020 outbreak of the new coronavirus.
Says the 2008 book End of Days predicted the current coronavirus outbreak.
entity_strings: End of Days, current coronavirus outbreak

text: A post shared on Facebook claims to show a 1956 video that seemingly predicts the COVID-19 pandemic, saying: Experts predict that by the year 2020, a new virus will rise, spreading from somewhere in Asia to the rest of the world.
